properties.name: zcy.redis.conf.cluster.max-redirects
properties.description:
Maximum number of redirects to follow when executing commands across the
 cluster.

properties.name: zcy.redis.conf.cluster.nodes
properties.description:
Comma-separated list of "host:port" pairs to bootstrap from. This represents an
 "initial" list of cluster nodes and is required to have at least one entry.

properties.name: zcy.redis.conf.database
properties.description: Database index used by the connection factory.

properties.name: zcy.redis.conf.password
properties.description: Login password of the redis server.

properties.name: zcy.redis.conf.pool.max-active
properties.description:
Max number of connections that can be allocated by the pool at a given time.
 Use a negative value for no limit.

properties.name: zcy.redis.conf.pool.max-idle
properties.description:
Max number of "idle" connections in the pool. Use a negative value to indicate
 an unlimited number of idle connections.

properties.name: zcy.redis.conf.pool.max-wait
properties.description:
Maximum amount of time (in milliseconds) a connection allocation should block
 before throwing an exception when the pool is exhausted. Use a negative value
 to block indefinitely.

properties.name: zcy.redis.conf.pool.min-idle
properties.description:
Target for the minimum number of idle connections to maintain in the pool. This
 setting only has an effect if it is positive.

properties.name: zcy.redis.conf.sentinel.nodes
properties.description:
Comma-separated list of "host:port" pairs to bootstrap from. This represents an
 "initial" list of sentinel nodes and is required to have at least three entry.

properties.name: zcy.redis.conf.share-native-connection
properties.description:
lettuce客户端共享连接配置，默认为true；请谨慎修改这个参数！！！
 true：表示共享redis连接，但是在blpop阻塞命令\事物操作中，会新建连接；这种方式占用连接数少，性能比jedis客户端高、稍微比连接池版本性能低点；
 false：表示每次去factory去获取连接的时候，都会新建连接；
